            <title>[LOG4J2-3014] Log4j1ConfigurationConverter on Windows produces &quot;&amp;#xd;&quot; at end of every line</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LOG4J2-3014</link>
                <project id="12310790" key="LOG4J2">Log4j 2</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When I run&#160;Log4j1ConfigurationConverter on Windows, the resulting xml file has &quot;&amp;#xd;&quot; at end of every line, e.g.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;    &amp;lt;Root level=&quot;DEBUG&quot;&amp;gt;&amp;amp;#xd;
      &amp;lt;AppenderRef ref=&quot;Console&quot;/&amp;gt;&amp;amp;#xd;
      &amp;lt;AppenderRef ref=&quot;RollingFile&quot;/&amp;gt;&amp;amp;#xd;
    &amp;lt;/Root&amp;gt;&amp;amp;#xd; &lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I found a bit of previous discussion about it here:&#160; &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LOG4J2-1528?focusedCommentId=15470100&amp;amp;page=com.atlassian.jira.plugin.system.issuetabpanels:comment-tabpanel#comment-15470100&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LOG4J2-1528?focusedCommentId=15470100&amp;amp;page=com.atlassian.jira.plugin.system.issuetabpanels:comment-tabpanel#comment-15470100&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
